service.tut.pori.contentanalysis

Class PhotoList

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.ResponseData
      • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.PhotoList
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeletedPhotoList, DissimilarPhotoList, ReferencePhotoList, SimilarPhotoList

    public class PhotoList
extends ResponseData
    This is a container class for photo elements, which can be used directly with Response to provide XML output.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<mediaList>
  <media>
    <credits>KwGZilfORbxRYDnRJOOATeERkgKQobENXDvDyLmWWWZtwTEQXzQZUamJazFZyZfP</credits>
    <description>pLPMXalhsjkVJrXVvEytTkYQxEIZdRMhbqsYgmAwreCmHedvLJpZOsjwgcBptpfL</description>
    <UID>afc8c96c-6523-4bff-9c74-87630156b47e</UID>
    <name>pnmKDeNIVVrTTAtrNtUdCnUlZyZRODEQtbNgYLcDDDFUxYzaCcKdovSDPQoUwBKr</name>
    <serviceId>1</serviceId>
    <visibility>PUBLIC</visibility>
    <objectList>
      <object>
        <backendId>105334350</backendId>
        <confidence>0.04171823869280289</confidence>
        <mediaObjectId>7381899336412632613</mediaObjectId>
        <mediaType>PHOTO</mediaType>
        <objectId>YYaxNjxnhtaFSuJuOCJAJNtAGAthZdrDurOmWsALajqputefKTPIBwXrNlPNwHoO</objectId>
        <rank>754453812</rank>
        <serviceId>6</serviceId>
        <status>NO_FRIENDLY_KEYWORD</status>
        <objectType>KEYWORD</objectType>
        <value>OTcKUADumreJKzkcbJlDllSyqrXnxEkbxDiuQVvXbejHPJZaVZlSWoRgHbTCjCFz</value>
        <visibility>PRIVATE</visibility>
        <userId>8291827787728071338</userId>
      </object>
    </objectList>
    <mediaType>PHOTO</mediaType>
    <userId>8291827787728071338</userId>
    <url>http://fe.example.org/rest/carc/r?uid=afc8c96c-6523-4bff-9c74-87630156b47e&amp;service_id=1</url>
  </media>
</mediaList>
